    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo describes methods of transporting Chinese characters in Internet services which transport text, such as electronic mail [RFC-822], network news [RFC-1036], telnet [RFC-854] and the World Wide Web [RFC-1866].  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  It does not specify an Internet standard.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
